        html: `<p><a title="Reading: Quick Reference" href="https://www.howtostudykorean.com/?page_id=237">Quick Reference:</a>&nbsp;Forget how to read? Don&rsquo;t worry! Take a look at the letters below and get them back into your memory!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Also available in:&nbsp;<a href="https://www.howtostudykorean.com/unit0/reading-quick-reference/turkish/">T&uuml;rk&ccedil;e</a>,&nbsp;<a href="https://www.howtostudykorean.com/unit0/unit-0-lesson-3/kurdish/">کوردی</a>&nbsp;,<a href="https://www.howtostudykorean.com/unit0/reading-quick-reference/kurdish/"><span lang="bg" title="Bulgarian language text">العربية</span></a></p>`,
